edu.harvard.integer.common.discovery

Class SnmpLevelOID

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.integer.common.BaseEntity
      • edu.harvard.integer.common.discovery.SnmpLevelOID
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDInterface, java.io.Serializable

    @Entity
public class SnmpLevelOID
extends BaseEntity
    These objects are used to identify the OIDs starting at the top level of a physical or virtual entity when the Entity MIB or other standard containment model is not used.

    There will always be one (potentially) many SnmpServiceElementTypeDiscrininator instances associated with an instance of this object. The Discriminator instances take the value returned from the contextOid to determine the service element type.
